<paragraph id="E9437E972BB93349CF450E908089AD81" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Sumpf-Ampfer</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="C96FEB2D356D6049C13C27C077F86073" pageId="null" pageNumber="732" type="description">
<paragraph id="2C41F3E38303371049B3ACB71E725620" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="4A9047BFD211A70FF8A83594C2F195E9" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Polygonaceae" genus="Rumex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="732" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="maritimus">
<emphasis id="DC9E5B8D59944FC7782523097E8D5DC7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">R. maritimus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 16) durch folgende Merkmale: 1- oder 2 
<normalizedToken id="8BC5DD0CE899C3CD2549BFC82B8943D6" originalValue="jährig" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">jaehrig</normalizedToken>
; 
<emphasis id="291F9BEBCFEF0FE26C7B7EE129E3C5CD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">
<normalizedToken id="3B55E0702E2605E53391AB1E8237CF40" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
zur Fruchtzeit braun bis 
<normalizedToken id="D10581EC22464F7F6BFE998F792147A9" originalValue="rötlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">roetlich</normalizedToken>
, nie goldgelb; die 
<normalizedToken id="0867716CBF0A18C75E4AB7D80E6809A0" originalValue="längsten" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">laengsten</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="6817D72C5587374C5F569CF73492BCC4" originalValue="Zähne" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Zaehne</normalizedToken>
am Rande der innern 
<normalizedToken id="F83353D2D3840E37674E9988C6C0EC31" originalValue="Perigonblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Perigonblaetter</normalizedToken>
nicht 
<normalizedToken id="063070737EFC1476713622CE63E65B8E" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">laenger</normalizedToken>
oder nur wenig 
<normalizedToken id="A11FCAD64D82CE21A16FD9FB5FB40D0A" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">laenger</normalizedToken>
als die 
<normalizedToken id="27361596737E3E95F0BCDF7CEADAA2D6" originalValue="größte" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">groesste</normalizedToken>
Breite
</emphasis>
(ohne 
<normalizedToken id="B0DA95FC8C8654E4808998506D70C6F5" originalValue="Zähne" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Zaehne</normalizedToken>
) 
<emphasis id="C08C63BDEB3E98A1CC8609A2CFA70C67" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">
der innern Perigon 
<normalizedToken id="626050F53492692AA4D9753016194D10" originalValue="blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">blaetter</normalizedToken>
. -
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="D0F30B0A672075EA3B7BEF43484FDFE5" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer bis Herbst.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C8FAB754D533B243967C3D2A115F232F" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">
<emphasis id="EFE408A864AAEC1368466994EBB5BEFA" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">
<pageBreakToken id="152E8D339D975803A6232231F264B402" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Zytologische</pageBreakToken>
Angaben. 2n
</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="A159BE3AAD89DB133488206EA395C3B3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">40:</emphasis>
Material ohne Herkunftsangabe (Jaretzky 1928), aus Skandinavien (
<normalizedToken id="38A62DB18ABC951DA8019543F8F7FE01" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Loeve</normalizedToken>
1942).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="730D07B4CFA9343468B8CE613C414A38" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">
<emphasis id="8E08005EBCB3E5137DE71130E7229017" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Standort.</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="2830B08E0AE14920E5C2F672AF3FBEB5" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Polygonaceae" genus="Rumex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="732" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="maritimus">
<emphasis id="69C45682DFF2B698A5996784980E4F1A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">R. maritimus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 16).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="788EE96741302BECAD4DBC7885B40890" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">
<emphasis id="B8D4714CD7C5CB7D4050609A5538BCFE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">
Verbreitung. Allgemeine Verbreitung wie 
<taxonomicName id="282B9F02B6956921D5C2D11AEFA66BE5" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Polygonaceae" genus="Rumex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="732" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="maritimus">R. maritimus</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
(Nr. 16); wenig Angaben aus Asien, da oft nur als 
<normalizedToken id="1273B1E916C4AF294878BFD026FEBACE" originalValue="Varietät" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Varietaet</normalizedToken>
von 
<taxonomicName id="7C4ED3AEAD74A4DABEF7A27C6D0DFA3C" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Polygonaceae" genus="Rumex" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="732" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="maritimus">
<emphasis id="E1C634785268EC89EA9EFCDD9D7CFE70" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">R. maritimus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
abgetrennt. - Im Gebiet: 
<normalizedToken id="530C5C0C2C92E3D21CA1428425C2EB93" originalValue="Französischer" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Franzoesischer</normalizedToken>
Jura (Etang de Meix bei Abergement-St-Jean), 
<normalizedToken id="8C7956E47EB4EC8D368E434CCEC1B522" originalValue="Elsaß" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Elsass</normalizedToken>
(Bachbett der Ill bei Meyenheim und 
<normalizedToken id="6238A03F7BA68986AB6AB3C94D377898" originalValue="Réguisheim" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">Reguisheim</normalizedToken>
; vgl. Kunz 1966), 
<normalizedToken id="BB4EECA73EE8A6209DB1892387520BC3" originalValue="früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="732">frueher</normalizedToken>
Vorarlberg (Bregenz).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
